        <title type="html"><![CDATA[MZ세대 65.4% "정규직 아니래도 괜찮아…프리랜서 의향"]]></title>
        <id>https://newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20220228_0001775391&amp;cID=13001&amp;pID=13000</id>
        <link href="https://newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20220228_0001775391&amp;cID=13001&amp;pID=13000"/>
